Treetasks - Organize tasks in an hierarchical format

Dependencies (python libraries):
        - anytree

Usage:
        The application is inspired by tudu and uses similar concepts and workflows. For keybindings reference, take a look at the cheatsheet provided in the repository. At the moment, you have to manually load the application in a python script. An example of how to do that is given in main.py.

        There will be missing features and bugs. Feel free to report them, but keep in mind that this is an alpha development version.
